hopobject.body: Could I borrow your phone, please? healthy-world.biz Even in her mug shot, celebrity chef Cat Cora managed to look picture perfect. The "Around the World in 80 Plates" host was snapped looking sleek and well-styled in a booking photo released by the Santa Barbara Police Department for her June 17 DUI arrest, which she got after a breathalyzer test revealed she had twice the legal limit of alcohol in her bloodstream after rear-ending another vehicle.
